PURE SUX by CodeRipper /ROi
---------------------------

Coded for DEMO.DESIGN 128b intro compo. 128 bytes of _pure_ sux ;)

[ESC]  - change effect
[CTRL] - exit to DOS

Tested on my 486DLC40/CL5422 and Slash's 486DX4-100/CL5430.

Yes, I know it's possible to decrease size down to ~80-100 bytes. 

e.g., change:

mov ax,03 
with 
mov al,03. 

replace 

xor cl,cl
label: 
[..] 
inc cl 
cmp cl,3 
jnz label

with 

mov cl,2
label:
[...]
dec cl
jnz label

etc...

But I'll better drink another one cup of tea (not beer!) 

